{"tid":712460,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼日利亞發力不容忽視，冰島泊大巴悶焗完場","createTime":"2018-06-22T06:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T04:00:49.000Z","uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0025568734c044899c8af60f0d9f9b6ecc33bb7a","tid":712460,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"睇見阿根廷昨晚狀態不佳 ， 尼日利亞自覺出線有一絲曙光 ，今晚尼日利亞 一定會出盡全力去取得勝利 ，搏盡無悔。<br />\n<br />\n冰島面對強攻相信會採取死守策略， 參考過往對陣紀錄 ，估計會悶局收場。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷球迷今晚不需氣餒， 正所謂鷸蚌相爭阿根廷得利， 不論比賽結果如何 都對阿根廷出線有利。 雖然痛失首名出線 ，但次名出線在望。 球迷不必擔心。 <br />\n球王美斯痛定思痛 ， 經過幾日沈殿 ，一定重拾信心，下星期帶領阿根廷戰勝尼日利亞， 踢一場好波給大家看。"},{"pid":"e1c59b83d4e12c8feb4252319bb6c40f99f5a067","tid":712460,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持美斯"},{"pid":"1d4cbcf0b519826efacdfc2c52f5de46f43c9fdd","tid":712460,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"美斯會帶領阿根廷戰勝尼日利亞"},{"pid":"9539f0b4f8efbe0793451c3714dd6026667e3afb","tid":712460,"uid":392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/161856_9042fde6cd7f4596751fb20080c2c6a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F161856_9042fde6cd7f4596751fb20080c2c6a3.png&h=b6300d56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d21822d8daad257a4decb3ec4589c2c43dabf3b","tid":712460,"uid":133873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"可以買大波波"},{"pid":"2aa82463c31a8d24b837ddc1c300d885b020127f","tid":712460,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"冰島今次就狂攻"},{"pid":"de93670d70eba6aa8b1d642c5ef8448e4c8be85a","tid":712460,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T01:56:48.000Z","msg